    "name": "Say No! More",
    "steam_appid": 1191900,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191900/extras/a4ebe4a6795693eb5403806877540d30.poster.avif?t=1759331341\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191900/extras/a4ebe4a6795693eb5403806877540d30.webm?t=1759331341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191900/extras/a4ebe4a6795693eb5403806877540d30.mp4?t=1759331341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>一款来自Studio Fizbin工作室的充满新意的游戏。在一个人人都安于现状、只会说“YES”的世界，你将创建自己的角色，作为一名实习生去履行肩负的使命——让世人学会说“不”，由此改变世界。有了这个神力，你将变得势不可挡，用“不”回敬一个个无理要求。<br><br>《Say No! More》是世界首款NPG（说NO！扮演游戏）。使用轻松上手的简单操控，在一家奇怪的公司开始既定的职业生涯。除了用自己的语言说“不”，你还能以不同的情绪说“不”，让敌人失去方寸。用不同的回应让对方混乱，放松警惕，然后积蓄你的能量，向猝不及防的同事来一个铆足劲的“不”！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191900/extras/7c2b30105e0f74b5bc494b99c728be3f.poster.avif?t=1759331341\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191900/extras/7c2b30105e0f74b5bc494b99c728be3f.webm?t=1759331341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191900/extras/7c2b30105e0f74b5bc494b99c728be3f.mp4?t=1759331341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏还将探讨现代社会的普遍问题，比如社会礼仪、友谊、职场环境等，看似诙谐搞怪的游戏背后也有一定的深度。一切都以九十年代后期的电子游戏风格呈现，加上鲜艳厚实的色彩，幽默的动画及爵士乐，让你难以说“不”。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191900/extras/f4baadc8737571d382cc159422b0627c.poster.avif?t=1759331341\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191900/extras/f4baadc8737571d382cc159422b0627c.webm?t=1759331341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191900/extras/f4baadc8737571d382cc159422b0627c.mp4?t=1759331341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191900/extras/9e3d6cb802cd9e7959b6f6587fd61835.webp?t=1759331341\" width=600 height=55 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>选择如何说“不”！激动的不！冷漠的不！慵懒的不！癫狂的不！<br></li><li>蓄力后再说“不”以获得更强效果！<br></li><li>惹毛你的同事！嘲笑他们！对他们拍手！向他们说“嗯……”！假装听他们说话，然后出言相讽！<br></li><li>用很多种语言说“不”！<br></li><li>定制你的角色！<br></li><li>和尖酸刻薄的同事、主管以及老板斗智斗勇！<br></li><li>利用午休时间交朋友！<br></li><li>大声欢笑，因为这个游戏太有趣了！<br></li><li>收听<strong>酷炫的混音带<br></strong></li><li>学会说“不”，向说不专家们看齐（比如下面这个家伙👇）</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191900/extras/db290d994cba02524f735f1d3e140420.poster.avif?t=1759331341\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191900/extras/db290d994cba02524f735f1d3e140420.webm?t=1759331341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1191900/extras/db290d994cba02524f735f1d3e140420.mp4?t=1759331341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
